data.description:
Welcome to Austin! We're excited to share with you a fantastic FURNISHED property that aligns perfectly with your needs. Our charming home, located at 7840 Portland Trail, offers a spacious, comfortable beds, towels, linens and creatively decorated living space, and we think you'll love it.

We understand the importance of finding a peaceful and inviting space to call home. This 3-bedroom, 2-full bath home is designed to provide you with the relaxation you deserve. The unique musical ambiance, with art and band posters adorning the walls, adds a touch of creativity to the atmosphere (especially our Willie Nelson Wall!).

Here are some key features of the property:

Size: 1,343 square feet
Bedrooms: 3
Bathrooms: 2 full baths
Location: Close to Q2 Soccer Stadium, The Domain Shopping Center, Apple Campus, More than 5 hospitals, and the Cedar Park HEB Center (for the music lover in you). 
Equipped with comfort: 2 Queen beds, 2 twin beds, and a sleeper sofa. Enough room for 7 to sleep comfortably. Refrigerator, Washer and Dryer, coffee maker.

But that's not all! We also want to let you know that our home comes with a convenient doggie door, making it a haven not just for you but also for your furry friend, if you have one. Dogs are more than welcome here, and we're thrilled at the possibility of having them join the vibrant atmosphere of our musical home.

If you're looking for a place that not only meets your practical needs but also welcomes you with that charming Austin flair, 7840 Portland Trail could be the perfect fit. Please don't hesitate to reach out for more details or to schedule a viewing. We can't wait to show you around and discuss how this home can cater to your wants and needs.

Renter pays utilities, which will be kept in the Landlord's name, unless tenant rents for over 6 months.\
3 months minimum lease, up to 2 years.
1 month security deposit is required. ($3500)
Non-refundable Pet Deposit Required ($100)
$50 application fee paid to Landlord to review the tenant's application.
No smoking cigarettes allowed inside property.

Once the application is received by the Landlord, the tenant selection criteria and the grounds for which the rental application may be denied, including the applicant's:
(1)criminal history;
(2)previous rental history;
(3)current income;
(4)credit history; or
(5)failure to provide accurate or complete information on the application form.

*Landlord is a Licensed Realtor in the State of Texas and representing personal property.
